@startuml Sequence_UC17
title UC-17: Kelola Stock Opname

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Stock Opname\n(livewire/hitung)" as View
participant "Hitung\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Hitung Model" as HitungModel
participant "HitungDetail Model" as DetailModel
participant "MaterialDetail Model" as MatDetailModel
participant "InventoryLog Model" as LogModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /hitung
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT hitungs ORDER BY hitung_date DESC
DB --> Component: Daftar stock opname
Component --> View: Render daftar sesi opname

== Mulai Stock Opname ==
User -> View: Klik Mulai Stock Opname
View -> Component: create()
Component -> HitungModel: Hitung::create(['hitung_number'=>..., 'status'=>'Draft', 'user_id'=>$userId])
HitungModel -> DB: INSERT INTO hitungs

Component -> DB: SELECT material_batches JOIN material_details
DB --> Component: Semua batch aktif
loop Setiap batch
  Component -> DetailModel: HitungDetail::create(['hitung_id'=>..., 'material_id'=>..., 'material_batch_id'=>..., 'quantity_expect'=>...])
  DetailModel -> DB: INSERT INTO hitung_details
end
Component --> View: Redirect ke halaman rincian opname

== Isi Hasil Aktual ==
User -> View: Isi quantity_actual setiap bahan
View -> Component: updateDetail($detailId, $actual)
Component -> DetailModel: HitungDetail::find($id)->update(['quantity_actual'=>$actual])
DetailModel -> DB: UPDATE hitung_details
Component --> View: Tampil selisih diperbarui

== Selesaikan Stock Opname ==
User -> View: Klik Selesaikan Stock Opname
View -> Component: finish()
Component -> DetailModel: HitungDetail::where('hitung_id',...)->get()
DetailModel -> DB: SELECT hitung_details
loop Setiap item dengan selisih negatif
  Component -> MatDetailModel: Sesuaikan supply_quantity
  MatDetailModel -> DB: UPDATE material_details
  Component -> LogModel: InventoryLog::create(['action'=>'hitung',...])
  LogModel -> DB: INSERT INTO inventory_logs
end
Component -> HitungModel: $hitung->update(['status'=>'Selesai','is_finish'=>true])
HitungModel -> DB: UPDATE hitungs
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

@enduml
